- id: JOURNAL-SCRIBE-STABILISATION-FINALE-20260601
  date: 2026-06-01
  mode: CRITICAL
  agent_type: cli
  surface: scribe-tooling
  titre: Scribe stabilisation finale
  objectif: >
    Stabiliser le bundle SCRIBE sans nouvelle feature ni modification applicative: baseline, getpid, TTL claims, tests critiques, ratio causal, simplification docs et backup final.
  hot_entries_consulted:
